# AccountingManager Comment Immutability

- All existing comments in `AccountingManager` partial classes are immutable.
- Do not remove, rewrite, reflow, relocate, or "clean up" any existing comment text.
- Do not change punctuation, casing, whitespace formatting, or wording of existing comments.
- Do not convert comment style (single-line to block, block to single-line, etc.).
- Code changes must be made around comments while preserving comment blocks exactly as authored.
- If a requested code change cannot be completed without modifying an existing comment, stop and ask the user for explicit approval first.

